                     </persName>
                      
                   on the Highway, putting him in Fear, and taking from him a Penknife and 35s. his Goods and Money, and an Iron Key
            </rs>, the Property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17330112-26-victim232" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Shute 
                  <interp inst="t17330112-26-victim232" type="surname" value="Shute"></interp>
